\[\|\widehat{\mathbb{E}}_{y}[v^{\theta}]-\mathbb{E}[v^{\theta}(Y)]\|\leq\frac{ C}{\sqrt{n}}\sqrt{\sigma_{\theta}^{2}(Y)+\frac{K^{2}}{n}}\log(2\delta^{-1})\]

