\[\mathbb{E}Z^{m}\leq\left(\mathbb{E}Z^{2(m-2)}\right)^{1/2}\left(\mathbb{E}Z^{ 4}\right)^{1/2}\leq 4K_{3}^{2}\sigma_{\theta}^{2}(X)^{2}\left(\mathbb{E}Z^{2(m-2) }\right)^{1/2}.\]

